OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,FThe father of a 21-year-old who was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death on Primrose Hill has
OL,9,Fsaid he has "nothing to live for", as
OL,10,Fpolice continue to investigate the
OL,11,Fkilling.
OL,13,FFinbar Sullivan died last Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening after a fight broke out at the
OL,15,Fpopular beauty spot in North London.
OL,17,FOfficers have been examining footage
OL,18,Fcirculating online which appears to
OL,19,Fshow the moments leading up to the
OL,20,Fstabbing.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
