OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,FIn his first television interview
OL,8,FChristopher Sullivan, Finbar's father,
OL,9,Ftold ITV News London about his horror
OL,10,Fafter receiving a call that his son
OL,11,Fhad been stabbed and attempts to save
OL,12,Fhim were failing.
OL,14,FHe rushed to the scene.
OL,16,F"I asked them, can you just let me
OL,17,Fthrough? Let me go. Go and see my son.
OL,18,FI've got to see my son.
OL,20,F"I just want to hold his hand before
OL,21,Fhe dies.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"And then they said - get away for the
OL,8,FCID. And then I knew. When the CID
OL,9,Fcame they said 'Mr. Sullivan, your
OL,10,Fson's dead'.
OL,12,F"He had bled to death. He'd been
OL,13,Fstabbed - I think from behind"
OL,15,FChristopher and Finbar lived alone
OL,16,Ftogether in Maida Vale. The grieving
OL,17,Ffather said they were "like best
OL,18,Ffriends".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"We did everything together. We went
OL,8,Fon holiday, just me and him together.
OL,9,FWe went away to see my mum in Wales
OL,10,Ftogether. We'd watch films together."
OL,12,FChristopher is now left to face a loss
OL,13,Fthat he says is "completely surreal".
OL,15,F"It happened to such a wonderful
OL,16,Fperson. And I'm sure every parent says
OL,17,Fthis, but when all his friends were
OL,18,Fhere, all the people that have come
OL,19,Fround here, they've all reiterated
OL,20,Fwhat I thought - that he was very
OL,21,Fspecial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"And everybody thinks their child is
OL,8,Fspecial. I'm not saying he's better
OL,9,Fthan anybody else, but he had all
OL,10,Fgenuine character traits.
OL,12,F"They said he was humble and he was -
OL,13,Falways. He said the other week "you're
OL,14,Fmore than a dad to me. You're my best
OL,15,Fever friend.
OL,17,F"I couldn't live without you" and vice
OL,18,Fversa. And I don't know how I carry
OL,19,Fon. Everything - everything - was
OL,20,Ftaken away from me."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,FMr Sullivan also criticised the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police, and Commissioner
OL,9,FSir Mark Rowley. He told ITV News
OL,10,FLondon:
OL,12,F"I'd say you're (Sir Mark Rowley)
OL,13,Fdoing a terrible job. If there'd been
OL,14,Fpolice on the street, this wouldn't
OL,15,Fhave happened. They should have had a
OL,16,Fdozen policemen just going, walking
OL,17,Faround the park. Why not? If they, if
OL,18,Fthey just on a rotation, they would at
OL,19,Fleast stop the fight. They would at
OL,20,Fleast get to Finn, before he died,
OL,21,Fwhere were they?
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with Finbar's
OL,9,Ffamily and friends for their
OL,10,Fdevastating loss. A man is in court
OL,11,Ftoday charged with his murder.
OL,13,F"We understand the concern this
OL,14,Fincident has also caused in the wider
OL,15,Fcommunity and have increased the
OL,16,Fnumber of officers on patrol in
OL,17,FPrimrose Hill to provide reassurance
OL,18,Fand respond to any offending.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"Our Royal Parks officers have been
OL,8,Fintegrated into local community
OL,9,Fpolicing teams. In Camden, a dedicated
OL,10,Flocal neighbourhood team regularly
OL,11,Fpatrols Primrose Hill and surrounding
OL,12,Fareas."
OL,14,FAn investigation remains underway.
OL,16,FChristopher issued a warning to young
OL,17,Fpeople to avoid violence and knife
OL,18,Fcrime. He is urging teens to think
OL,19,Fabout the consequences of their
OL,20,Factions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"I'd say to them - give it up, because
OL,8,Fthere's no future in criminality. I
OL,9,Fthink all they have to do is look at
OL,10,Fthe list of their friends. Dead. Dead.
OL,11,F20 years in prison. 20 years in
OL,12,Fprison. Just look at it from a
OL,13,Fcompletely pragmatic point of view and
OL,14,Fjust consider."
OL,16,FChris and Leah are now parent
OL,17,Fgrieving, Finbar was their only son.
OL,18,FChris also had a message to parents
OL,19,Fwho may be concerned their child could
OL,20,Fbe carrying a knife:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776164568
OL,3,C'You're doing a terrible job': Father
OL,4,Cof stab victim criticises Sir Mark
OL,5,CRowley
OL,7,F"I can't say be careful because my son
OL,8,Fwas in the most innocuous place in
OL,9,FBritain. So it can happen at any time.
OL,11,F"But I would say to those that have
OL,12,Fchildren that might use knives, search
OL,13,Fthem before the way out, make sure
OL,14,Fthey don't have knives, because I'll
OL,15,Ftell you one thing, you do not want to
OL,16,Flook around one day and realise that
OL,17,Fyou created this thing that's given me
OL,18,Fthis pain and has destroyed someone's
OL,19,Flife because it's not just his life.
OL,20,FYou've destroyed about 50 lives."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
